Adds two keyboard shortcuts to swap the windows tiled to the left and right, and top and bottom halves respectively of the screen.

To set the shortcuts to trigger the action: go to [i]System Settings[/i] > [i]Shortcuts[/i] > search for [i]Swap halves[/i] > set your preferred shortcuts.

For more information on installation and configuration as well as any requests, please visit [url=https://github.com/nclarius/KWin-window-geometry-scripts/tree/main/swap-halves]the GitHub page[/url].

